com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc
Class IDocDocumentList

java.lang.Object
  com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc.IDocDocumentList
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocumentList, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, java.io.Serializable
public class IDocDocumentList
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocumentList, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable

Class that holds and manages a list of IDoc documents using JCoIDocDocumentList to implement the IDocDocumentList interface.

Wraps the JCoIDoc implementation, so that documents can be saved or transferred to another SAP Adapter. If you work on a JCoIDocDocumentList, make sure that you do create a IDocDocumentList, that wraps it. After that you can put this object as iDocList into the pipeline.

public IDocDocumentList(com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocumentList jcoDocumentList)
Creates a document list using the passed JCoIDocDocumentList. New documents can be added corresponding to the IDoc repository used for this document list.

jcoDocumentList - A document list that should be wrapped for use on the SAP Adapter.
